I fixed changing the models to return the BigQueryHook like you did, but I didn't knew if it was the best choice and I didn't changed the db.py.
Thanks a lot!

ping @ashb  @Acehaidrey @bolkedebruin  @mistercrunch  @Fokko 
Hi all, I want to get at least one other (more the merrier) committers + some users on board with this PR as it is a big change. Hopefully can have it merged by end of week unless major concerns are identified. I have bad unit test/pep8 left to fix (almost there), but no code change otherwise. 

@mistercrunch do you have release access for FAB ? if not I can ping the owner. Thanks!

Well this issue was duplicated again in https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/AIRFLOW-2160 and was fixed in #3081. 
Weird that the iterdecode function doesn't come up in my search on github (and still doesn't: https://github.com/flask-admin/flask-admin/search?utf8=%E2%9C%93&q=CHAR_ESCAPE&type=). Guess I won't use github's search function anymore. 

@ashb, @bolkedebruin, and @Fokko thanks for taking the time to look at this. Let me know if you want the tests I wrote for this specific problem, otherwise this PR can be closed.
